commentTextItems.html: sweeps down past the keeper to the fence.

commentPostTextItems.html: Pakistan win by 7 wickets and lead the series 4-0. Akmal and Butt were off to a flier and set the tone for an easy win for Pakistan. Butt played well for his 70. The highlight of the match being Shakib-Al-Hasan's knock of 108, he build his innings wonderfully, he picks up the Man-of-the-Match award.
Thanks for being with us, please do join us for the final ODI on April 19. Until then it is bye from all of us here at Cricinfo. I am Binoy George and along with Raymond signing off.
